Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,中国是世界上最神秘的国度之一
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,China is one of the most fascinating countries in the world, 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.39,0:01:09.35,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,历史，传统与日新月异的科技在此交融碰撞
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.39,0:01:09.35,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,a place where history, tradition, and rapid innovation collide.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这里既是人类最古老文明的摇篮
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,This place is home to some of humanity's oldest civilizations, 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,同时也坐落着宛如未来之城的都市
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.74,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and at the same time, to cities that look like they were built for the future.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.05,0:01:22.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然而，正如中国的现实世界广袤而独特
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.05,0:01:22.07,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But just as China's physical world is vast and unique, 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.07,0:01:24.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,其数字空间亦是如此
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.07,0:01:24.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,so is its digital world, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,与大多数国家不同
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Unlike most countries, 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.00,0:01:29.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,中国的互联网并非运行于我们所熟知的全球平台之上
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.00,0:01:29.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,China's internet doesn't run on the same global platform as many of us are used to.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.44,0:01:34.81,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它拥有自成一派的系统，服务器，乃至应用程序
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.44,0:01:34.81,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Instead, it has its own system, its own servers, and even its own apps.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,微信取代了WhatsApp
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.15,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,WeChat instead of WhatsApp, 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.15,0:01:40.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,微博取代了Twitter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.15,0:01:40.57,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Weibo instead of Twitter, 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.49,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而抖音则取代了TikTok
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.49,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and Douyin instead of TikTok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.49,Yahei-1920x1080,atg3,0,0,0,,其实是一家的
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,数十亿用户每日连接于此
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Billions of users connected every day
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.80,0:01:50.21,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,构成一个几乎与西方世界完全割裂的线上生态圈
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.80,0:01:50.21,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,, on an online ecosystem that exists almost entirely apart from the West.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.81,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这种隔绝造就了某些非凡之物
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.81,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,This separation has created something remarkable.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个让潮流，社群，乃至都市传说都以一种外界罕见的方式演进的空间
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A space where trends, communities, and even myths evolve in ways the rest of the world rarely sees.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.74,0:02:10.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而在那些流转于中国各大论坛，社交媒体，以及早期互联网低语中的无数故事里
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.74,0:02:10.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And within those countless stories that circulate across Chinese forums, social media, and whispers on the early internet, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有些因其绮丽，悲怆与可怖而脱颖而出
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.29,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,some stand out from their beauty, their tragedy, and their horror.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,其中一个流传最久远的故事始于二十世纪九十年代中期
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.30,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,One of the most enduring stories begins in the mid-1990s, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.99,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在北京的顶尖学府，清华大学
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.99,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,at Beijing's prestigious Tsinghua University.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,故事围绕着一位才华横溢的年轻学子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.70,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It starts with a gifted young student, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.13,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一场突如其来的神秘疾病
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.13,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,a sudden, mysterious illness, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,以及一次为挽救她而做出的绝望尝试
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.11,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and a desperate attempt to save her 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.11,0:02:36.34,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这次尝试后来成为了中国互联网最早的伟大谜案之一
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.11,0:02:36.34,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,that would make history as one of the first great mysteries of the Chinese internet.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当大多数人想到九十年代的中国时
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,When most people think of China in the 1990s, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们脑海中浮现的是一个向世界敞开大门的国家
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,they picture a country opening its doors to the world.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,摩天大楼在北京和上海拔地而起
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.65,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Skyscrapers, rising in Beijing and Shanghai.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.96,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但在这场变革的浪潮之下
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.96,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But behind that transformation, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.71,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,互联网才刚刚崭露头角
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.71,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,the internet was only just beginning to take shape.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,大学的主干网络，研究服务器
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.30,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,University backbones, research servers, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,以及连接中国与世界的第一批谨慎链路
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and the first cautious connections linking China to the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.47,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而正是在这个脆弱的早期网络上
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.47,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And it was through this fragile early network 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这个国家最黑暗的谜团之一即将揭晓
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,that one of the country's darkest mysteries would unfold.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.31,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,故事始于北京的清华大学
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.31,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,We started at Tsinghua University in Beijing, 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个素有“中国麻省理工”之称的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,often called China's MIT.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.15,0:03:18.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一位名叫朱令的二十一岁学生是这一切的中心
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.15,0:03:18.42,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A 21-year-old student named Zhu Ling was at the center of it all,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.09,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她在化学领域才华出众，亦在音乐上天赋异禀
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.09,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,brilliant in chemistry, gifted in music.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.19,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,朋友们记得她弹奏着古老的古琴
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.19,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Friends remembered her playing the ancient Guqin, 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在北京音乐厅的灯光下演出
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.73,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,performing pieces under the lights of the Beijing concert hall.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.65,0:03:32.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但在1994年底，她的生命轨迹却开始分崩离析
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.65,0:03:32.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But in late 1994, her life began to unravel.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.23,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,起初只是些微不足道的症状，胃痛和疲惫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.23,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,At first it was small things, stomach pain, and exhaustion.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后，她开始脱发
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And then the hair loss started.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.51,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,几周之内，她那头乌黑亮丽的长发已然脱落殆尽
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.51,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Within weeks, her long black hair was gone.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,医生们辗转于各大医院
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Doctors cycled through hospitals, 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.44,0:03:48.84,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,试图寻找一个合理的解释，自身免疫性疾病，病毒感染
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.44,0:03:48.84,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,searching for explanation, autoimmune diseases, viral infections.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但无一吻合
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But nothing fit.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,到了1995年春天，朱令逐渐陷入瘫痪
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.76,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,By the spring of 1995, Zhu Ling was slipping into paralysis.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她的身体一寸寸地失控
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Her body falling piece by piece.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,直至陷入昏迷
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.07,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Until she fell into a coma.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她的同学们心急如焚
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.25,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Her classmates were desperate.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在一个没有谷歌，没有Reddit的时代
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.66,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,In an era before Google, before Reddit, 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.31,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们做了一件当时几乎无法想象的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.31,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,they did something almost unthinkable for the time.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们将她的故事发布到了互联网上
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.76,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They took her story to the internet.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.59,0:04:17.61,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,1995年4月10日，学生们在Usenet
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.59,0:04:17.61,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,On April 10, 1995, students posted an SOS to Usenet, 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个早期的在线论坛上，用英文详述了朱令的怪异症状，发布了一封求救信
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.76,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,one of the earliest online forums detailing Zhu Ling's strength symptoms in English.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们恳求任何可能识别这种病症的人伸出援手
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They begged for help from anyone who might recognize the pattern.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.14,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,接下来发生的事情如今已成为传奇
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.14,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And what happened next is now legendary.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,回复如潮水般从世界各地涌来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Replies came pouring in from across the world.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那些素未谋面的医生和专家们，却都洞察到了同一个危险信号
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.87,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Doctors and specialists who have never even met her, but saw the same red flag.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.03,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,铊中毒
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.03,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Thallium poisoning.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.49,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一种罕见而致命的重金属
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.49,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A rare and deadly heavy metal.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,症状分毫不差
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.67,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The exact symptoms matched.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.16,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,神经损伤，腹部剧痛
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.16,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Nerve damage, abdominal pain, a
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,乃至她指甲上的苍白纹路
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.40,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,nd even the pale lines on her fingernails.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.32,0:04:53.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,全世界的智慧诊断出了一个中国顶尖医院都束手无策的病例
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.32,0:04:53.02,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The world had diagnosed a case that China's top hospitals had missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:53.02,Yahei-1920x1080,atg3,0,0,0,,协和医院早先“排除铊中毒”可能性，事后拒绝承认朱令为铊中毒\n详情参阅百度百科“朱令事件”或维基百科“朱令铊中毒事件”
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.23,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,到了五月，北京的医生们终于为她进行了检测
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.23,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And by May, doctors in Beijing finally tested her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.23,Yahei-1920x1080,atg3,0,0,0,,引用自维基百科：\n由于互联网上的回信怀疑是铊中毒，当朱令父母得知\n北京市劳动卫生职业病防治研究所的陈震阳教授可做铊中毒鉴定后\n在一位协和医生的暗中帮助下，取得朱令的尿液，脑脊液，血液，指甲和头发\n于1995年4月28日来到北京市劳动卫生职业病防治研究所进行检验\n测定显示，“所有标本中均有很高的含铊量，高于健康人千百倍\n从而铊中毒的诊断得到证实。”
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,结果证实了是铊中毒
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Thallium was confirmed.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们争分夺秒地进口解药
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.88,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They scrambled to import the antidote.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,解药奏效了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.11,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And it worked.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但仅仅是堪堪赶上
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But only just in time.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,1995年8月31日，朱令从昏迷中苏醒
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.75,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,On August 31, 1995, Zhu Ling woke up from her coma.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她活了下来，但伤害已不可逆转
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,She had survived, but the damage was permanent.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.36,0:05:17.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她的视力，记忆和行动能力都已支离破碎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.36,0:05:17.02,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Her vision, memory, and movement were all shattered.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,从此，她的父母成为了她的照料者
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.75,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,From then on, her parents became her caretakers, 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,背负着她本该拥有的璀璨人生的重量
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.41,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,carrying the weight of life she could have lived.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但故事并未就此结束
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the end of the story.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.69,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它只是另一个谜团的开端
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.69,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It was only the beginning of another mystery.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.79,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,究竟是谁对她下的毒手？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.79,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Who poisoned her?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,嫌疑最终落在了她的一位室友身上
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.67,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Suspicion landed on a roommate.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她是为数不多能在实验室接触到铊的人之一
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.57,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,One of the few with axes of thallium in a lab.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她接受了讯问，但从未被起诉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,She was questioned, but never charged.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,多年来，有关方面的沉默只让揣测的火焰愈烧愈旺
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.72,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And over the years, the silence of authorities only fueled speculation.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.91,0:05:49.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在网上，朱令的名字成为了一声抗议的呐喊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.91,0:05:49.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Online, Zhu Ling's name became a rallying cry protest.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.39,0:05:54.83,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,请愿，无休止的辩论，以及那些悬而未决的问题，其意义甚至超越了案件本身
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.39,0:05:54.83,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Petitions, endless debates, and unanswered questions became bigger than the case itself.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个人怎能在大庭广众之下犯下如此罪行而逍遥法外？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.40,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,How could someone get away with this in plain sight?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,几十年后，法医科学提供了一条令人不寒而栗的线索
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Decades later, forensic science offered a haunting clue.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,研究人员分析了朱令保存下来的几缕头发
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Researchers analyzed strands of Zhu Ling saved hair.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.08,0:06:10.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们如同绘制年轮一般
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.08,0:06:10.66,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They mapped the thallium concentrations like tree rings, 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.66,0:06:13.99,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,标绘出头发中的铊浓度，揭示了长达数月的持续性投毒
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.66,0:06:13.99,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,showing a pattern of repeated poisoning over months, 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.19,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,并在她倒下前有一次剧烈的剂量爆发
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.19,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,followed by a sharp burst right before her collapse.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.38,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是蓄意所为，是有人干的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.38,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It was deliberate that someone had done this.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.24,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但始终无人为此承担罪责
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.24,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But still, no one was held responsible.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,朱令一直活到了2023年
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Zhu Ling lived until 2023.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在北京去世，享年五十岁
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.10,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,She died in Beijing at 50 years old.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在承受了近三十年的苦难之后
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,After nearly three decades of suffering.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.25,0:06:38.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当消息传来，那个曾拯救过她的互联网，再一次为她哀悼
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.25,0:06:38.27,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,When the news broke, the internet that had once saved her, mourned her again.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不仅是为那被窃取的人生，也为那永未浮出水面的真相
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.30,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Not just the life that was stolen, but the truth that never surfaced.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,时至今日，朱令的故事被铭记为一个转折点
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.45,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And today, Zhu Ling's story is remembered as a turning point.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.45,0:06:51.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,借由线上陌生人的集体智慧，得以解决的首例重大医疗案件
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.45,0:06:51.76,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The first major medical case solved through the collective knowledge of strangers online.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它证明了互联网能够拯救生命
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Proof that the internet could save lives.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.89,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,同时，也提醒着我们它的局限
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.89,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,At the same time, it's a reminder of its limits.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.91,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为纵然有数百万人齐心协力为她诊断
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.91,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Because while millions of people came together to diagnose her,
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,即便是互联网，也未能将正义送达
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.72,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,not even the internet could deliver the justice.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.79,0:07:36.67,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,In the late 2010s, as livestream culture exploded across China, 
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.79,0:07:36.67,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,10年代末，直播文化迅速席卷中国
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.67,0:07:39.69,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,one figure rose higher than almost anyone else.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.67,0:07:39.69,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,有一个主播，可以说是“会当凌绝顶”
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.31,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Literally.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.31,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,字面意义上的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.72,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,His name was Wu Yongning.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.72,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,此人名叫吴永宁
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.65,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And he called himself a rooftopper.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.65,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,自称「rooftopper」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.65,Default-#1-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,*rooftopper没有约定俗成的翻译\n意思是拍摄高空极限视频的人
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.65,0:07:51.85,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,A performer who scaled skyscrapers, cranes, and towers without ropes or safety gear.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.65,0:07:51.85,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,主打不用安全绳徒手攀登摩天大楼、塔吊和高塔
Dialogue: 2,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.79,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Bouncing on edges where a slip meant death.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.79,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在高空建筑的边缘上表演各种特技
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.69,0:08:00.10,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Wu had grown up poor with dreams of becoming an actor.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.69,0:08:00.10,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,吴永宁出身贫寒，梦想是成为演员
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.10,0:08:04.27,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,He did stunt work in local films, even martial arts shows, 
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.10,0:08:04.27,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,他在当地的影视剧，和武术表演中当过特技演员
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.43,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,but never found steady success.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.43,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,均未获得成功
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.55,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,What he did find was, was a phone, 
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.55,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,但他另辟蹊径，拿起手机
Dialogue: 2,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.85,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, an audience, and a niche.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.85,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,给爱看跑酷的观众直播
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.35,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And by 2017, 
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.35,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,到2017年
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.35,0:08:18.67,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, his short videos of death-defying climbs were going viral on platforms like Huo Shan and Weibo.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.35,0:08:18.67,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,他拍摄的极限攀爬短视频，在火山和微博等平台上爆火
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.86,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Thousands tuned in to see him hanging one-handed from a ledge of a 40-story tower.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.86,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,无数人涌进直播间，只为看他单手悬挂40层高楼的外沿
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.46,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Or tiptoeing across beams thinner than his own shoes.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.46,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,或者看他走过比鞋还窄的钢梁
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.42,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,To his fans, he was fearless.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.42,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在粉丝眼中，他无所畏惧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.27,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And to his critics, he was reckless.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.27,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在黑子们眼中，这是没脑子
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.11,0:08:42.25,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But behind that persona was pure pressure.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.11,0:08:42.25,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,网络世界的光鲜亮丽背后，蕴藏着巨大压力
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.32,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Livestream platforms in China had turned danger into revenue, 
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.32,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在直播平台眼里，他的特技越危险，收益越高
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.79,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,likes, donations, and contracts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.79,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,点赞、打赏、合同
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.43,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, tied to stunts he had to outdo the last.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.43,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,都与他能否超越上一次的极限表演挂钩
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.83,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Wu was only 26 years old, supporting his family, 
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.83,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,那时吴永宁只有26岁，肩负着养家的重担
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.83,0:08:59.13,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,hoping to marry his girlfriend and promising bigger feats to sponsors.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.83,0:08:59.13,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,还要和女友结婚，答应赞助商带来更惊险的表演
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.13,0:09:02.00,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The higher he climbed, the more he needed the risk.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.13,0:09:02.00,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,他只能往更高、更危险的地方爬
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.23,0:09:09.49,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,On November 8th, 2017, Wu traveled to Changsha in the Hunan Providence.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.23,0:09:09.49,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,2017年11月8日，吴永宁来到湖南长沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:09.49,Default-#1-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,*吴永宁是湖南宁乡人
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.48,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The Huayuan International Center was one of the tallest buildings in the city.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.48,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,挑战长沙最高的建筑之一，「华远国际中心」
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.14,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,62 stories of glass and steel.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.14,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,整整62层的玻璃与钢筋
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.31,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He carried his phone, set it up to record, and went to work.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.31,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他把手机架好、打开录像，开始表演
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.69,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The footage, later confirmed by authorities, 
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.69,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,录像经警方证实为真
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.69,0:09:27.14,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, showed him attempting his most dangerous stunt yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.69,0:09:27.14,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,记录了他最危险的一次挑战
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.14,0:09:32.15,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Pulling himself up from the outer ledge of the tower, dangling over 200 meters in the air.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.14,0:09:32.15,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在200米高楼的外沿做引体向上
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.00,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,He raised himself once, twice, 
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.00,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,一次、两次
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.18,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,and on the third try, his arm trembled.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.18,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,第三次，手臂开始颤抖
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.22,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,His grip started to slip.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.22,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,他的手已经抓不紧了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.63,0:09:43.50,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,He clawed to the edge for 4 or 5 seconds, 
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.63,0:09:43.50,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,就这样拼命硬撑了4、5秒
Dialogue: 2,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.65,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and then... he fell.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.65,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后...掉了下去
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.48,0:09:52.10,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Wu Yongning's phone captured it all.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.48,0:09:52.10,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,吴永宁的手机记录下了全部过程
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.13,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And when the news broke weeks later, reactions were conflicted.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.13,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,几周后消息传出，舆论相当两极化
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.36,0:10:00.23,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Fans mourned. Others scolded him for recording death.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.36,0:10:00.23,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,粉丝为他哀悼，也有人指责他拿死亡当表演
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.23,0:10:05.21,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,His girlfriend revealed he had been hoping to win enough in sponsorships to propose marriage.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.23,0:10:05.21,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,后来吴永宁的女友透露，他是想拿够赞助商的钱娶她结婚
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.08,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Officials condemned rooftopping as illegal, life-threatening behavior.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.08,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,上面谴责这种极限攀爬行为违法，且极度危险
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.82,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And platforms tightened restrictions on livestream stunts.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.82,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,各大平台也开始收紧直播特技的规定
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.98,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But the legacy lingered.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.98,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,但他的影响仍未消散
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.29,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Wu Yongning became both a martyr and a warning.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.29,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,吴咏宁成了一个殉道者，一个警示
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.92,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,China's first and most famous rooftoper.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.92,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,中国第一位、也是最著名的rooftoper
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.40,0:10:26.52,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,He turned skyscrapers into a stage, till the stage claimed him.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.40,0:10:26.52,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,摩天大楼就是他的舞台，却因舞台而亡
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.86,0:11:04.85,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,In January 2022, a short video surfaced on Douyin, the Chinese version of TikTok.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.86,0:11:04.85,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,2022年1月，抖音上出现了一个短视频
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.63,0:11:09.55,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The footage came from Feng County, in Jiangsu, Providence.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.63,0:11:09.55,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,视频拍摄于江苏徐州的丰县
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.73,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And it immediately went viral.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.73,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,瞬间引爆网络
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.14,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The clip is simple.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.14,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,内容很简短
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.14,0:11:16.27,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,A man walks into a small shed with a pot of food.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.14,0:11:16.27,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,男子端着一锅食物，走进简陋的小屋
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.27,0:11:20.22,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Sitting inside is a woman, chained by her neck.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.27,0:11:20.22,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,屋子里坐着一个女人，脖子上拴着铁链
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.22,0:11:23.89,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,She looks thin, disoriented, and confused.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.22,0:11:23.89,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,女人身体瘦削、神情恍惚，目光涣散
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.10,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Next to her, on the floor, are basic bedding and housing items.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.10,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}地上铺着简陋的被褥和生活用品
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.59,0:11:33.23,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Very quickly, it was discovered that this woman was the mother of eight children.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.59,0:11:33.23,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,很快，人们就发现女人竟然生了8个孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.09,0:11:40.03,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The video spread across Douyin, Waibo, and Bilibili at lightning speed.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.09,0:11:40.03,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,视频在抖音、微博、B站等平台上直接爆了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.70,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Generating outrage.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.70,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,激起网民众怒
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.70,0:11:45.85,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Millions of comments began asking, why is she chained?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.70,0:11:45.85,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,无数评论质问道“为什么要把她锁起来？”
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.91,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And how is she the mother of so many children?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.91,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,“为什么她会生这么多孩子？”
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.11,0:11:54.52,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Authorities in Feng County first claimed that the woman suffered from mental illness.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.11,0:11:54.52,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,丰县当地政府的说法是，该女子患有精神疾病
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.52,0:11:59.17,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And was being cared for by her husband, a local farmer named Dong Zhimin.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.52,0:11:59.17,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,她的丈夫董志民在当地务农，一直照顾着她
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.01,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But those answers only created more questions.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.01,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,质疑之声接踵而至
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.59,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,If she was mentally ill, why was she raising eight children?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.59,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,如果她精神失常，怎么可能养8个孩子？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.79,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And why is she chained up in a freezing shed
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.79,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,为什么要把她锁在寒冷的棚屋里
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.41,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, instead of treated at a hospital?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.41,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,而不是送去医院？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.72,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Within days, internet users uncovered further details.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.72,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,没多长时间，网友便挖出了更多细节
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.46,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Her name was Xiaohuamei.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.46,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,女子名叫小花梅
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.86,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And many began to suspect that she was a victim of human trafficking.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.86,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,很多人怀疑她是董志民买来的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.51,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Independent volunteers traveled to Feng County, 
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.51,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,有一些人自发前往丰县
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.08,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,filming the shed and confirming the chain.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.08,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,拍下了棚屋，证实脖子上的铁链是真的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.08,0:12:30.17,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Their videos were quickly deleted as they were posted.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.08,0:12:30.17,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,视频刚发出来就被光速下架
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.97,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But the mirrors never stopped.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.97,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,但是补档绝不缺席
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.20,0:12:37.52,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The pressure grew so large that officials had to release new statements.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.20,0:12:37.52,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,舆论压力越来越大，当地政府不得不多次发布新通告
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.40,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Each one contradicting the last.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.40,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,里面的说法自相矛盾
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.60,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,First, they denied the trafficking.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.60,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,一开始说她不是拐卖来的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.60,0:12:46.84,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Then they admitted issues brought from another Providence under unclear circumstances.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.60,0:12:46.84,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,然后又说她是外省拐到这儿的，具体情况不明
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.03,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And finally, after weeks of backlash, 
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.03,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,数周后，在舆论持续发酵下
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.03,0:12:57.33,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,they admitted that multiple people were involved in moving her illegally across providences.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.03,0:12:57.33,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,ZF才承认，这起跨省拐卖案牵涉到多人
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.56,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And that her documentation had been falsified.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.56,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,她的身份证和户口也是假的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.61,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Several local officers were later punished for negligence.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.61,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,随后几名政府官员因工作不当被处分
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.88,0:13:10.72,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But despite the reports, not all details were ever clarified.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.88,0:13:10.72,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,即便如此，还是有很多不为人知的细节
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.61,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Who exactly sold her?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.61,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,人贩子是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.61,Default-#1-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,实际上调查出来了，是时立忠、桑合妞等人
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.37,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,How long has she been chained?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.37,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,小花梅被关了多久？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.63,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And why did it take a viral video for intervention to happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.63,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,为什么要等到视频火了才有人管？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.16,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Many of these questions remained unanswered.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.16,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,这些问题都没有答案
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.12,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The viral Douyin video forced nationwide attention.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.12,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,那段抖音视频引起全国关注
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.44,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,It sparked conversations on women's rights, 
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.44,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,它引发了关于女性权利
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.44,0:13:31.85,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, human trafficking, and rural poverty in China.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.44,0:13:31.85,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,人口拐卖，以及中国农村贫困问题的讨论
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.85,0:13:36.99,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Hashtags were censored, posts were deleted, and yet the story spread further.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.85,0:13:36.99,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,ban掉相关话题、贴子后，反而越传越广
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.99,0:13:41.45,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Even international media outlets like the BBC and the New York Times picked it up.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.99,0:13:41.45,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,连BBC和《纽约时报》等海外媒体都开始报道
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.54,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Implifying the clip outside of China.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.54,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,让这段视频传到了国外
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.29,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The image of a woman chained by her neck, 
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.29,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,脖子上套着铁链的女人
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.60,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, staring blankly at the camera, became a symbol.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.60,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,呆滞地看向镜头，成了一种象征
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.56,0:13:54.25,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,For many, it was proof of hidden suffering in rural China.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.56,0:13:54.25,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,对许多人来说，那就是中国农村不为人知的苦难
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.26,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,For others, it showed the power of a single short video
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.26,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,还证明了短视频的力量
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.57,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,to break through censorship and expose a hidden crime.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.57,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,突破审查限制，让罪行重见天日
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.57,0:14:05.26,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And even now, years later, the original clip is extremely hard to find.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.57,0:14:05.26,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,多年过去，原版视频已经很难找到了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.93,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But the outrage never fully disappeared.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.93,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,但是愤怒 从未消散
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.18,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The chain woman in Fang County remains one of the darkest
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.18,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,丰县“铁链女”事件，依然是中国互联网历史上最黑暗
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.49,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} and most disturbing viral videos in Chinese internet history.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.49,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最令人不安的现象级视频之一
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.95,0:14:47.05,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,In the vast landscape of Chinese internet oddities, 
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.95,0:14:47.05,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在中国互联网广阔的离奇事件中
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.37,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,some entries are so bizarre they feel almost like urban legends.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.37,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,有些离奇得像都市传说
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.42,0:14:55.44,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,One of these is simply titled, The Man and His Telephone.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.42,0:14:55.44,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,其中一个是《人与电话》
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.00,0:14:59.61,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And at first glance, that sounds mundane, almost boring.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.00,0:14:59.61,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,光看名字倒是没啥
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.61,0:15:02.41,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The clip it refers to is anything but that.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.61,0:15:02.41,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,视频内容可不是
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.01,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,It isn't a surveillance footage or it's not found film.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.01,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,这并非监控录像或「已找回媒体」
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.16,0:15:13.11,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,It's actually a skit performed by Chen Peisi, one of the most famous comedians in China.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.16,0:15:13.11,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,而是中国著名喜剧演员陈佩斯表演的小品
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.68,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Throughout the 1980s and 1990s, 
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.68,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在上世纪八九十年代
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.58,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,, Chen was a household name, 
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.58,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,陈佩斯可以说是家喻户晓
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.37,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,loved for his sharp wit and slapstick performances.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.37,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,以犀利的幽默和夸张的肢体喜剧深受喜爱
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.14,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Which is exactly what made this particular video so unsettling.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.14,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,正因如此，才显得短片如此诡异
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.89,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The premise is simple, a man sitting with his telephone.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.89,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,故事很简单，就陈佩斯坐在电话面前
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.78,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,But as the minutes pass, it begins to unravel.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.78,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,然后，诡异的事情越来越多
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.57,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,The ringing of the phone drives him into madness.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.57,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,电话不停的响，快把陈佩斯听疯了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.94,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Slowly, until the comedy vanishes.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.94,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,然后短片就跟喜剧没什么关系了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.17,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And what should have been in just another sketch, 
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.17,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,一个普通的小品
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.73,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,takes on a surreal, almost nightmarish quality.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.73,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,朝着超现实、灵异的方向展开
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.43,0:15:48.92,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Viewers have described it as feeling like analog horror wrapped in everyday reality.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.43,0:15:48.92,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}观众形容，它更像是披着日常外壳的「模拟恐怖」
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.76,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,A familiar figure, a familiar object, suddenly soared into something uncanny.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.76,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,日常生活中再常见不过的人和物，忽然变得诡异陌生
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.07,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And what makes this even stranger is its scarcity.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.07,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,更奇怪的是，这段视频极为罕见
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.07,0:16:02.10,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Despite Chen's immense fame, this performance is rarely aired.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.07,0:16:02.10,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,虽然陈佩斯很有名，但《人与电话》几乎没有重播过
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.72,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,It's even harder to find online.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.72,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,在网上更稀有
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.46,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And for decades, it slipped under the radar, 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.46,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,几十年来，这部短片悄无声息
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.20,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,till fragments started resurfacing on Chinese forums.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.20,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,最近几年才零零散散的出现在中国的论坛里
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.95,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Some interpret it as satire of modern life.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.95,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,有些人认为短片讽刺了现代生活
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.51,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Or a metaphor for technology's suffocating presence.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.51,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,还有人说这是隐喻现代科技无孔不入，令人窒息
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.50,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Others swear that there's something darker at play.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.50,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至有人相信背后藏着更黑暗的秘密
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.50,0:16:25.76,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Why else would a clip featuring one of China's most beloved comedians be so difficult to track down?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.50,0:16:25.76,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,不然，为什么陈佩斯这种大腕演的短片会如此难找？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.32,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,Why would it appear, then disappear, 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.32,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,为什么它总是出现又消失
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.35,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,as if someone wanted it to be buried?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.35,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,像是被刻意隐藏起来？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.31,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,And whether intentional or not, the effect is chilling.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.31,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,无论这是不是刻意为之，效果都令人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.31,0:16:38.89,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,It blurs the line between comedy, psychological breakdown, 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.31,0:16:38.89,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,它模糊了喜剧与心理崩溃之间的界线
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.02,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,between performance and possession, 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.02,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,也模糊了表演与失控之间的界线
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.10,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,a man alone with his telephone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.10,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,一个孤独的男人，对着电话
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.08,Default-L2-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} unraveling in front of an audience.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.08,Default-Import3,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在观众面前走向崩溃
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,﻿2022年末，在吉林省
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.20,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,In late 2022, Jilin Providence
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一名少女在凌晨时分
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,a teenage girl was caught on a CCTV
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,被监控拍到正走在一座桥上
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,walking across a bridge in early morning hours.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,接着，她就凭空消失了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.70,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And then, she simply just vanished.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,没有留下一丝一毫的踪迹
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.70,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,No exit and no trace.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,女孩名叫郑春梅，年仅十八岁
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The girl's name was Zheng Chunmei, only 18 years old.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,监控录像记录的内容非常简单
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The video is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:48.00,Yahei-1920x1080,atg3,0,0,0,,本段监控录像为吉林市另一起失踪案件，应为原作者查找资料时的失误
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.92,0:17:48.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,凌晨四点刚过，女孩进入了画面，径直走过桥梁
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.92,0:17:48.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,She enters the frame walking alone across a bridge, just after 4 a.m.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,桥面空空如也，街道一片寂静
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.40,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The bridge is empty the streets are quiet
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而她却再也没有走出摄像头的视野
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and then she never leaves the camera's view.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她没有从马路对面向前走出来
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.32,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,She doesn't come out on the other side of the road.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她也没有掉头
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.50,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,She doesn't turn back
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她就这么消失了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.05,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,she's just gone.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.35,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,监控录像引发了大规模的搜寻
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.35,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The footage sparked massive search
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.35,0:18:09.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,警方救援队和志愿者把河道和周围的街道翻了个底朝天
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.35,0:18:09.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,police rescue teams and volunteers comb the river in the surrounding streets.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们检查了过往车辆
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.90,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,They checked passing vehicles
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,并逐帧观察了周围区域的录像
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,they reviewed every frame of the footage around the area.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但无论调查团搜寻得有多仔细
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But no matter how closely they looked
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,都始终得不出一个明确的答案
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.72,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,there was no clear answer.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人认为她跳进了河里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Some believe she jumped into the river
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但尸体却一直没有被发现
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.75,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,there no body was ever recovered.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,另有人提出了谋杀的可能性
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.25,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Other suspected foul play
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,说或许是有人在摄像头盲区里截住了她
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,that someone may have intercepted her off camera.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然而谜题却没能得到解释
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But the mystery remained
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,另一台理应记录下事情全过程的摄像头
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.70,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,one camera that should have explained what happened
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,却没有展露出丝毫异常
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,instead showed nothing at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在网上，阴谋论迅速传播开来
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Online theories spread fast
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人认为录像被动了手脚
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.17,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,some argue the footage have been tampered with
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,部分帧被剪辑过，或者被模糊处理了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.67,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,that certain frames are cut or blurred out.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有人提出了更超自然的解释
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Others pushed more supernatural explanations
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,说她可能是走去了另一个维度
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.32,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,that she'd walked into another dimension
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或者说，河流以超乎人类认知的方式吞噬了她
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.22,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,or that the river claimed her in ways beyond human explanation.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,由于案件一直没能彻底被侦破
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.17,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Because the case was never fully solved
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,阴谋论的声量变得越来越大
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.82,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,these theories only grew louder.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,说起互联网恐怖
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.42,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,When you think of Internet horror
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,最具标志性的莫过于“后室”了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.75,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,one of the most iconic modern myths is the back rooms.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它于2019年左右在西方互联网兴起
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.60,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It started in the West around 2019
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.47,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,起初只是一条简简单单的蠕动意面帖子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.47,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,with a simple creepy pasta post.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,照片中是一个无边无际的黄色办公空间
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.90,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A photo of an endless yellow office space
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,潮湿的地毯，嗡嗡作响的日光灯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.87,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,damped carpets, buzzing fluorescent lights
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,若你脱离你所处的现实
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.65,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and promised that if you know clip out of reality
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就有可能被困在里面
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.72,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,you might find yourself trapped there.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,仅凭这一张图片
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.67,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And from that one image
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,“后室”便一举发展成了一整个互联网共创怪谈体系
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,the back rooms exploded into an entire Internet mythology.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,人们基于它创作了游戏、短片，乃至整个恐怖宇宙
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.82,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,People built games, short films, and entire universes of horror.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.47,0:19:56.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,所有这些都围绕着同一个核心理念：
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.47,0:19:56.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,All centered on the same idea
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,迷失在熟悉却又不对劲、无边无尽的阈限空间之中
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.77,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,being lost in endless, liminal space, that feels familiar but wrong.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但在中国，大家对这种理念的演绎更为独特
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.95,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But China has its own spin on the concept.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.63,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在中国最大的同性交友网站比比汗丽丽上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.63,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,On Bilibili, 
Dialogue: 2,0:20:07.63,0:20:11.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,创作者们开始尝试被称为“中国后室”的本土化创作
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.63,0:20:11.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,creaters begin experimenting with the known as the Chinese back rooms.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,乍一看，两种后室非常相似：
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.22,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,At first glance, they look very similar
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.22,0:20:15.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,长长的走廊、闪烁的灯光
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.22,0:20:15.12,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,long hallways, flickering lights
Dialogue: 2,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,以及那种“你不该出现在此地”的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.55,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and the feeling that you're somewhere you shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但其细节却具有鲜明的中国风格
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But the details are distinctly Chinese.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,没有了泛黄的壁纸和格子间
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.85,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Instead of the yellowish wallpaper and the cubicles
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.00,0:20:28.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,“中国后室”以废弃医院、昏暗的学校走廊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.00,0:20:28.25,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,the Chinese back rooms feature abandoned hospitals, darkened school corridors, 
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,以及上世纪90年代老旧的政府建筑为主要场景
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.65,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and outdated government buildings from the 1990s.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些地方几乎是每个中国人
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.37,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Their places almost everyone in China
Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在人生某个阶段都会遇到的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.77,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,have encountered at some point in their life.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,荒废的童年教室
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.55,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A child's classroom left behind
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一间似乎永远都不会变样的医院候诊室
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.20,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,a hospital waiting room that never seems to change.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有一个摆满了无穷无尽的灰色文件柜的政府办公室
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.12,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And a government office with endless grey filing cabinets.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一些创作者发掘的更深入一些
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Some creators have gone further
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,将这种风格与“鬼工厂”的概念融合
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.15,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,by blending this style with a ghost factory.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这种美学以巨大的工厂为主要元素
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,This aesthetic takes the king factories
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,将其呈现为无边无际的阈限空间
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.77,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and presents them as endless liminal spaces.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,对我而言，这正是中国后室如此迷人的关键之所在
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.27,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And to me, that's what makes the Chinese back rooms so fascinating.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它们表明，一个简单的概念
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.65,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,They show a single idea
Dialogue: 2,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,也就是“对无尽的阈限空间的恐惧”
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.70,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,the fear of an endless liminal space
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,会根据文化背景而演变
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.95,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,can evolve depending on culture
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在西方，是办公空间
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.82,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,in the west, its office spaces
Dialogue: 2,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而在中国，则是代表着日常生活的场所：
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.70,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and China is the institutions that define daily life
Dialogue: 2,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,医院、学校和工厂
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.52,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,hospitals, schools, and factories.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它们使人感到不寒而栗的方式各不相同
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.20,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Both are very unsettling in their own way.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,说实话，这正是这种本土化改编的绝妙之处
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.77,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And honestly, that's what makes this adaptation so cool.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它不仅仅是对西方互联网怪谈的简单复制
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It's not just a copy of Western Internet myth
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而是一种深刻的重新诠释
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.02,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,it's a reinterpretation.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它证明了“阈限恐怖”具有普遍性
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.67,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The one that proves liminal horror is universal
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,与此同时又深深植根于本土特色
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.77,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,but also deeply local.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,说到互联网上的恐怖内容
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,When we think of horror on the Internet
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.05,0:22:01.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,大部分人首先会想到油管
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.05,0:22:01.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,most of us turn to YouTube, 
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.87,0:22:05.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,像是《Local 58》或《曼德拉记录》这样的模拟恐怖系列
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.87,0:22:05.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,in a like horror series like Local 58 or the Mandela catalog, 
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.07,0:22:08.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,围绕着低保真的广播、诡异的信号和噩梦般的插播内容
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.07,0:22:08.67,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and our built entire communities around low five broadcast
Dialogue: 2,0:22:08.67,0:22:11.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,形成了完整的社区文化
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.67,0:22:11.62,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,crept as signals, and nightmares interruptions.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.12,0:22:15.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但咱中国人有自己的油管，噼里啪啦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.12,0:22:15.37,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But China has its own version of YouTube, BiliBili.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.65,0:22:17.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,尽管平台不同
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.65,0:22:17.37,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And although the platform is different
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,内容却有诸多相似之处
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.17,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,the content often feels familiar.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.57,0:22:22.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它有自己的烂梗、自己的网络文化
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.57,0:22:22.17,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It has its own memes, its own internet culture
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,以及自己的互联网恐怖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.50,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and its own horror.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.67,0:22:27.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,Bilibili 上最奇特的恐怖风格之一被称为“模拟恐怖”
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.67,0:22:27.82,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,One of the strangest sub-genres on BiliBili is called Simulated Horror.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.62,0:22:31.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它与我们西方人所说的“拟态恐怖”非常相似
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.62,0:22:31.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And it's very similar to analog horror we have in the west.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,“模拟恐怖”的核心主要有两个概念：
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.52,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,At the core of the Simulated Horror are two main ideas
Dialogue: 2,0:22:35.97,0:22:38.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,视觉劫持和电视插播
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.97,0:22:38.15,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,eye jackings and TV interruption.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,某些视频会有意模仿紧急广播
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,You'll see clips styled like emergency broadcast
Dialogue: 2,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,冷静的声线突然开始播报令人毛骨悚然的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.90,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,where a calm boy suddenly announces something terrifying, 
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,也许是关于某种怪物的警告
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,maybe a creature warning
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.45,0:22:47.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,也许是预警一种根本不存在的灾难
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.45,0:22:47.82,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,maybe a disaster that doesn't actually exist.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.67,0:22:50.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,另一种视频则模仿了失踪人口警报
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.67,0:22:50.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Another video is mimic missing person alerts
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在插播时段，一个孩子的脸会闪过屏幕
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.62,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,though setting interruptions, where a child's face flashes on screen.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但不同的是，这里的警报会出现故障、失真
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.02,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Except here, the alerts glitch, distort
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.02,0:23:00.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或传达毫无逻辑的信息
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.02,0:23:00.55,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,or deliver information that makes in those sense.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.05,0:23:04.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,之所以能吓到人，就是因为它让人感觉很真实
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.05,0:23:04.62,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It's a fear that works because it feels real.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.27,0:23:07.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些广播被设计得看起来非常拟真
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.27,0:23:07.55,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The broadcaster designed to look authentic
Dialogue: 2,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,足以让人误以为它们是
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.65,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,just believable enough that you can mistake them for something
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.65,0:23:12.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,政府真的播出过的内容
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.65,0:23:12.07,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,the government really aired.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,西方的拟态恐怖往往倾向于怀旧：
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.02,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Western interlock horror often leans on nostalgia
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.02,0:23:22.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,VHS画面、本地接入频道、充满年代感的图像
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.02,0:23:22.52,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,VHS screen, local access channels, aesthetic-filled screens.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.02,0:23:26.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它之所以可怕，是因为它看起来像过去的遗物
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.02,0:23:26.77,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It's scary because it looks like a relic of the past
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.77,0:23:30.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一件从90年代或80年代挖掘出来的，受损的“文物”
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.77,0:23:30.02,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,a corrupted artifact, pulled from the 90s or 80s.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:32.85,0:23:35.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,Bilibili 的“模拟恐怖”则让人感觉有所不同
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.85,0:23:35.20,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,BiliBili's Simulated Horror feels different.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些视频反映了生活在高度互联、被监控社会中的现实
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,These videos reflect the reality of living in a hyper-connected monitor society
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在这样的社会里，一次广播插播会让人感觉具有权威性
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.17,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,where a broadcast interruption feels authoritative
Dialogue: 2,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至事关生死
Dialogue: 1,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,or even life or death.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.37,0:23:47.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,最能代表模拟恐怖的作品之一
Dialogue: 1,0:23:45.37,0:23:47.37,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,One of the best examples of the sub-genre
Dialogue: 2,0:23:47.37,0:23:49.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,莫过于《雾潮来袭》（BV1pm4y1H7QL）
Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.37,0:23:49.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,is a clip called Fog Tide Incoming.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.37,0:23:52.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,视频开头就像真实的紧急播报一样
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.37,0:23:52.75,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,At first, it looks like a real emergency feed.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.80,0:23:57.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,公共安全广播警告居民，浓雾正席卷这座城市
Dialogue: 1,0:23:53.80,0:23:57.87,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The public safety broadcast warning residents that a heavy fog is rolling into the city
Dialogue: 2,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,并附带了分步的疏散指南
Dialogue: 1,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.95,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,accompanied by a step-by-step evacuation guidelines.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:01.97,0:24:02.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,表面上看
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.97,0:24:02.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And on the surface
Dialogue: 2,0:24:02.92,0:24:05.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它感觉和我们之前谈到的失踪人口插播
Dialogue: 1,0:24:02.92,0:24:05.40,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,it feels just as authentic as missing person interruptions
Dialogue: 2,0:24:05.40,0:24:08.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或被劫持的警报一样真实可信
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.40,0:24:08.15,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,or hijacked alerts we talked about earlier.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:08.85,0:24:10.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但两者还是存在区别的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:08.85,0:24:10.07,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But there's a difference.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:10.65,0:24:12.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那些逼真的插播
Dialogue: 1,0:24:10.65,0:24:12.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,There's realistic interruptions
Dialogue: 2,0:24:12.00,0:24:15.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,屏幕上闪过的失踪儿童啦，直播频道突发的劫持啦
Dialogue: 1,0:24:12.00,0:24:15.75,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,missing children's flashing on screen, sudden hijack needs of a live channel
Dialogue: 2,0:24:16.30,0:24:19.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,之所以令人恐惧，正是因为它们有可能发生
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.30,0:24:19.02,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,or terrifyingly precisely because they could happen
Dialogue: 2,0:24:19.02,0:24:21.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它们植根于现实之中
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.02,0:24:21.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,they're grounded in reality.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:21.75,0:24:25.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而《雾潮来袭》则更偏向虚构
Dialogue: 1,0:24:21.75,0:24:25.05,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Fog Tide Incoming, on the other hand, leads more into fiction.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:25.32,0:24:26.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,广播给出的指南毫无逻辑
Dialogue: 1,0:24:25.32,0:24:26.95,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The guidelines make no sense
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.95,0:24:29.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,仿佛指南的目的不是为了保护，而是为了伤害
Dialogue: 1,0:24:26.95,0:24:29.65,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,as if they were designed to harm rather than protect.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.77,0:24:32.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后，在播报的中途
Dialogue: 1,0:24:30.77,0:24:32.52,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And then, in the middle of the broadcast
Dialogue: 2,0:24:32.52,0:24:34.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个微笑的花朵头赫然出现
Dialogue: 1,0:24:32.52,0:24:34.85,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,a smiling flower head appears.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:35.50,0:24:38.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是任何真实的紧急播报中绝不会出现的内容
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.50,0:24:38.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Something no real emergency feed would ever include.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:05.82,0:25:08.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,同样让观众恐惧，但是以一种截然不同的方式
Dialogue: 1,0:25:05.82,0:25:08.15,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It's unsettling but in a different way.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:08.50,0:25:11.35,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它不再让人感觉像是井然有序的现实世界正在崩溃
Dialogue: 1,0:25:08.50,0:25:11.35,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Instead of it feeling like a real-world system breaking down
Dialogue: 2,0:25:11.75,0:25:14.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而更像是踏入了另一个完全不同的现实
Dialogue: 1,0:25:11.75,0:25:14.12,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,it feels like stepping into another reality altogether
Dialogue: 2,0:25:14.25,0:25:17.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在那里，广播本身成为了恐怖的征兆
Dialogue: 1,0:25:14.25,0:25:17.25,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,where the broadcast themselves become indices of horror.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:18.15,0:25:20.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,看到两种不同的文化和两个不同的平台
Dialogue: 1,0:25:18.15,0:25:20.60,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It's very interesting to see two different cultures
Dialogue: 2,0:25:20.60,0:25:22.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,衍生出同一个可怕的概念
Dialogue: 1,0:25:20.60,0:25:22.39,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and two different platforms
Dialogue: 2,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.59,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还挺有意思的
Dialogue: 1,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.59,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,but the same terrifying concept.